aywright.local.config.ts`\n- `test:e2e` → `bash scripts/run-e2e-local.sh` (full bootstrap → test → teardown)\n- `test:e2e:devnet` → `bash scripts/run-e2e-devnet.sh`\n\n**`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/package.json` (root)**\n- `test:visual` → `turbo run test:visual`\n- `test:e2e` → `pnpm --filter @rng-utopia/platform test:e2e`\n- `test:e2e:devnet` → `pnpm --filter @rng-utopia/platform test:e2e:devnet`\n\n### 5. Wallet Test Infrastructure\n\n**`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/WalletProvider.tsx`**\n- Purpose: Unified wallet provider with mode switching\n- Modes:\n  - Mock mode: `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true` → `MockWalletProvider`\n  - Test wallet mode: `VITE_TEST_WALLET=true` → `TestWalletWrapper` (lazy-loaded)\n  - Real mode: default → `RealWalletProvider` (lazy-loaded)\n- Exports: `WalletProvider`, `WalletContext` (re-exported from shared context)\n\n**Test Wallet Components**\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/TestWalletWrapper.tsx`\n  - Purpose: Reads 32-byte seed from `window.__TEST_WALLET_SEED__` and renders `TestWalletProvider`\n  - Throws if seed not found (injected by Playwright `addInitScript`)\n  - Lazy-loaded by `WalletProvider` when `VITE_TEST_WALLET=true`\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/TestWalletProvider.tsx`\n  - Purpose: Test wallet provider that signs real transactions with an injected Keypair\n  - Features: Auto-connect on mount (default: true), real transaction signing via `sendAndConfirmTransaction`\n  - Default RPC URL: `http://127.0.0.1:8899`\n  - Exports: `TestWalletProvider` component\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/index.ts`\n  - Purpose: Barrel export for test wallet components\n  - Exports: `TestWalletProvider` (only)\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/TestWalletProvider.test.tsx`\n  - Purpose: Unit tests for TestWalletProvider and MockWalletProvider\