rkspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/01-error-flow.spec.ts`\n  - Purpose: Error flow tests (insufficient balance, join unavailable match, settle already-claimed match)\n  - Tests: 3 serial tests with controlled failure scenarios\n  - Key exports: None\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/02-cancel-flow.spec.ts`\n  - Purpose: Cancel flow test (create → cancel → refund → lobby clears → recreate)\n  - Tests: 1 test with balance assertions for refund verification\n  - Key exports: None\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/03-lifecycle.spec.ts`\n  - Purpose: Full coinflip lifecycle test (create → join → resolve → claim)\n  - Tests: 1 comprehensive test with on-chain assertions for match state, treasury fees, player profiles\n  - Key exports: None\n\n**Devnet E2E Tests (Real Orao VRF)**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/devnet/smoke.spec.ts`\n  - Purpose: Devnet smoke tests (env validation, app loads, wallet connects)\n  - Tests: 3 tests (devnet deployments reachable, app loads against devnet, wallet connects with test keypair)\n  - Key exports: None\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/devnet/lifecycle.spec.ts`\n  - Purpose: Full devnet lifecycle test with real Orao VRF fulfillment\n  - Tests: 1 comprehensive test (create → join → real VRF → claim with dual polling strategy)\n  - Includes wallet funding helper and VRF polling with exponential backoff\n  - Key exports: None\n\n#### Fixture Files\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n  - Purpose: Shared visual regression fixture\n  - Key exports: `test` (extended with `stablePage`), `expect`\n  - Features: Seeds Math.random/crypto, freezes animations/transitions, collects console errors, waits for fonts\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/fixtures.ts`\n  - Purpose: Dual-browser-context fixture for local E2E tests\n  - Key exports: `test` (extended with `DualPlayerFixtures`), `expect`\n  - Fixtures: `playerAContext`, `playerBContext`, `playerAPage`, `playerBPage`, `playerAKeypair`, `playerBKeypair`, `connection`\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/devnet/fixtures.ts`\n  - Purpose: Dual-browser-context fixture for devnet E2E tests\n  - Key exports: `test` (extended with `DevnetDualPlayerFixtures`), `expect`\n  - Fixtures: `devnetConfig`, `playerAContext`, `playerBContext`, `playerAPage`, `playerBPage`, `playerAKeypair`, `playerBKeypair`, `connection`\n\n#### Helper Files\n\n**Local Test Helpers**\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n  - Purpose: Deterministic keypair generation and wallet funding\n  - Key exports: `PLAYER_A`, `PLAYER_B`, `LOCAL_RPC_URL`, `fundWallet()`, `fundTestWallets()`\n  - Seeds: `PLAYER_A` = 0xaa (32 bytes), `PLAYER_B` = 0xbb (32 bytes)\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/localnet-setup.ts`\n  - Purpose: Localnet initialization (coinflip/platform config PDAs, player profiles)\n  - Key exports: `ADMIN`, `TREASURY`, `initializeLocalnet()`, `ensurePlayerProfiles()`\n  - Seeds: `ADMIN` = 0xdd (32 bytes), `TREASURY` = 0xcc (32 bytes)\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/on-chain.ts`\n  - Purpose: On-chain assertion helpers (match PDA, treasury fees, player profiles)\n  - Key exports: \n    - Program IDs: `COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID`, `PLATFORM_PROGRAM_ID`, `FEE_BPS`\n    - PDA derivation: `getMatchPda()`, `getConfigPda()`, `getPlayerProfilePda()`\n    - Program instances: `getCoinflipProgram()`, `getPlatformProgram()`\n    - Fetch helpers: `fetchMatch()`, `fetchPlayerProfile()`, `getTreasuryAddress()`\n    - Balance helpers: `getBalanceLamports()`, `snapshotBalance()`\n    - Fee calculation: `calculateExpectedFee()`\n    - Assertions: `assertMatchCreated()`, `assertMatchClosed