aderboard.png, loot.png, lord-of-rngs.png, profile.png)\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/states.spec.ts/`\n  - 6 PNG screenshots (coinflip-connected.png, coinflip-disconnected.png, coinflip-error-toast-position.png, home-connected.png, home-disconnected.png, profile-connected.png)\n\n### 2. Playwright Configuration Files\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`\n  - Purpose: Default config for visual regression tests (mock mode)\n  - Test dir: `./e2e`, test match: `visual/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Web server: `pnpm dev` on port 3000, `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true`\n  - Viewport: 1280x1080, workers: 1, retries: 0\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts`\n  - Purpose: Real wallet mode tests (no blockchain interaction)\n  - Test dir: `./e2e`, test match: `real/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Web server: `npx vite --port 3001`, `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`, `VITE_RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com`\n  - Viewport: 1280x1080, workers: 1, retries: 0\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n  - Purpose: Local E2E tests against solana-test-validator\n  - Test dir: `./e2e`, test match: `local/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Web server: `npx vite --port 3002`, `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`, `VITE_TEST_WALLET=true`, `VITE_RPC_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8899`, `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK=localnet`\n  - Timeout: 60s, workers: 1, retries: 0, fullyParallel: false\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.devnet.config.ts`\n  - Purpose: Devnet E2E tests with real VRF fulfillment\n  - Test dir: `./e2e`, test match: `devnet/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Web server: `npx vite --port 3003`, `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`, `VITE_TEST_WALLET=true`, inherits RPC URL and program IDs from process env\n  - Timeout: 120s (for real VRF), workers: 1, retries: 0, fullyParallel: false\n\n### 3. Shell Scripts\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/localnet-bootstrap.sh`\n  - Purpose: Start solana-test-validator with coinflip/platform programs and Orao mock accounts\n  - Validates: Programs built (`coinflip.so`, `platform.so`, keypairs exist)\n  - Preloads: 3 Orao VRF mock accounts from `localnet-accounts/` directory\n  - Writes PID to `.localnet.pid`, ledger to `.localnet-ledger/`, logs to `.localnet-validator.log`\n  - Max wait: 30s for RPC readiness, fails with log tail on timeout\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/localnet-teardown.sh`\n  - Purpose: Stop solana-test-validator and clean temp files\n  - Reads PID from `.localnet.pid`, kills validator (graceful then force), cleans ledger and logs\n  - Flag: `--keep-logs` to preserve `.localnet-validator.log`\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/run-e2e-local.sh`\n  - Purpose: Single-entrypoint for local E2E tests\n  - Sequence: bootstrap → Playwright tests → teardown (always, even on failure)\n  - Returns exit code from Playwright tests\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/run-e2e-devnet.sh`\n  - Purpose: Single-entrypoint for devnet E2E tests\n  - Validates: `VITE_RPC_URL`, `VITE_COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID`, `VITE_PLATFORM_PROGRAM_ID` env vars\n  - No bootstrap/teardown (uses pre-deployed programs)\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/localnet-accounts/` (directory)\n  - Contains 3 JSON files with pre-loaded Orao VRF mock accounts:\n    - `orao-network-state.json` (pubkey: `5ER1oENnV4srxYdAynUfRzWeQCPQaqMiAp4VqyMbSqnK`)\n    - `orao-random-player-a.json` (pubkey: `S4ne8ejGPUwNMNsE8L7gtjbTaBLBfVGdWNH6VQrL58a`, randomness byte[0] = 2 → HEADS)\n    - `orao-treasury.json` (pubkey: `Ecs89dz8NsNoSxyUtp54G2HPbmvJr8qZnxnWUqiLT92r`, 10 SOL)\n\n### 4. Package.json Scripts\n\n**`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/package.json`**\n- `test:visual` → `playwright test` (uses default `playwright.config.ts`, m