letProvider` (only)\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/TestWalletProvider.test.tsx`\n  - Purpose: Unit tests for TestWalletProvider and MockWalletProvider\n  - Tests: 2 tests (TestWalletProvider auto-connects with keypair, MockWalletProvider starts disconnected)\n  - Uses vitest + @testing-library/react\n\n### Summary Statistics\n\n- **Total test spec files**: 9 (2 visual, 1 real, 4 local, 2 devnet)\n- **Total test scenarios**: ~22 distinct tests across all suites\n- **Playwright configs**: 4 (default/visual, real, local, devnet)\n- **Helper modules**: 7 (wallets, localnet-setup, on-chain, page-objects, env, vrf-polling, fixtures)\n- **Shell scripts**: 4 (bootstrap, teardown, run-e2e-local, run-e2e-devnet)\n- **Test wallet components**: 4 (TestWalletWrapper, TestWalletProvider, test unit, index barrel)\n- **Snapshot images**: 17 PNG files (11 routes + 6 states)\n- **Mock VRF accounts**: 3 JSON files (network-state, random-player-a, treasury)\n\nAll files are implementation-complete and production-ready. The infrastructure supports three distinct test modes: visual regression (mock), local integration (test-validator), and devnet integration (real VRF)."}],"totalDurationMs":164463,"totalTokens":89291,"totalToolUseCount":47,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1938,"cache_read_input_tokens":82190,"output_tokens":5156,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1938,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
